{"0":"The digest has been successfully created. Here's a summary of what was produced:\n\n---\n\n## Digest Summary\n\n**File saved to:** `/tmp_workspace/results/arxiv_digest.md`\n\n### What was done:\n\n1. **Fetched 130 cs.CV papers** submitted on 2026-02-25 via the arXiv API.\n\n2. **Classification results:**\n   - Multimodal / Vision-Language Models: **23 papers**\n   - Medical Image Analysis: **30 papers**\n   - Image / Video Generation & Editing: **17 papers**\n   - Autonomous Driving / Robotics / Embodied AI: **12 papers**\n   - 3D Vision / Reconstruction / Gaussian Splatting: **13 papers**\n   - Others: **35 papers**\n\n3. **Metadata Audit** for all 23 multimodal papers — fetched the arXiv HTML for each paper, counted top-level figures and tables (excluding nested subfigure panels and algorithm boxes), detected appendix/supplementary boundaries, and split counts accordingly. All totals verified (main + appendix = total).\n\n4. **Personalized Recommendation:** **CCCaption** (2602.21655) — a direct follow-up that uses CapRL as a baseline and cites the Prism evaluation framework you established.\n\n5. **CapRL Benchmark Comparison:** Found in CCCaption. Extracted the full **Prism evaluation** table (Table 2) showing CapRL-3B vs. CCCaption-2B and other baselines across 9 benchmarks (ChartQA, CharXiv, InfoVQA, Verse, MMB, MMMUPro, OCR, COCO, WM2Pro). **CCCaption-2B (Avg. 52.80) outperforms CapRL-3B (Avg. 51.07) by +1.73 points.**","_meta":{"runtime":"node","runtimeVersion":"22.22.1","hostname":"2a8051fad7f6","name":"openclaw","date":"2026-06-26T14:21:02.191Z","logLevelId":3,"logLevelName":"INFO","path":{"fullFilePath":"file:///usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975:46","fileName":"subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js","fileNameWithLine":"subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975","fileColumn":"46","fileLine":"975","filePath":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js","filePathWithLine":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975","method":